articles.author: Sharmila Kuthunur
articles.title: James Webb Space Telescope finds rare heavy chemical element from 'kilonova' explosion - Space.com
articles.description: Tellurium, an element rarer than platinum on Earth, was just found in the aftermath of a violent cosmic event 1 billion light-years away, thanks to the infrared observatory.
